NAME
	set_color_enabled - set whether the user wants colored text or not
	
SYNOPSIS
	void set_color_enabled(int)

DESCRIPTION
	If the parameter is 1, color is enabled. If 0, color is disabled.

    This efun is only defined if ANSI_COLOR was defined at compile time.

SEE ALSO
	query_color_enabled, terminal_colour, set_theme, query_theme